{
  "stem": "17625.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 115.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's-- so they, they, they, they, they kept him and brought him to our crematorium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also there was one was-- the name was, was [POLISH]-- [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- when I-- when I was joining the kommando, I heard that he was before also in the kommando.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But somehow, he was-- he was taken back to Auschwitz and they, they interrogated him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was-- he, he was political.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was political, and then he was against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He-- and then they brought him back and made him kapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then he was with, with my commander.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Together with Leizer, it was also he.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And once [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Crematorium 5 was built after the 2 and 3, so when they built the Crematoriums 4 and 5, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] everything was ready but electric was not ready.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was in the-- in the cook's place, there was a little window where the truck came to unload the-- it was a full-- a full-- a full room of cooks.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So once, it was in the evening, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I had something to hide, food which I, I had.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I put it in the cooks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this, this SS [POLISH]-- he wasn't an officer, a [INAUDIBLE] he was on the truck and his name was Kulsis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came in, he saw me there on the cooks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He grabbed me and-- to throw me out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know if he tells me to throw me out in the crematorium, that's the only way-- that's the only way to, to-- inside he can-- he can't do anything to me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he pushed me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- and I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Wladek was there, and he saved me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He saved me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
